cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.IR 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with HDR video reconstruction from raw sensor data. It may also belong to Multimedia (cs.MM) as it deals with video processing. Graphics (cs.GR) is another possible sub-category as it involves image and video rendering. Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Information Retrieval (cs.IR) are also possible sub-categories as the paper involves fitting local polynomial approximations to observed sensor data, which could be seen as a form of machine learning, and the output mapping could be seen as a form of information retrieval.
